        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is NeuronWriter?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">NeuronWriter is a content optimization platform that uses Natural Language Processing to analyze top-ranking pages and score your content in real-time (0–100). You paste a keyword, it pulls SERP results, identifies NLP terms, and tells you what to add. Think Surfer SEO at 80% less cost — with fewer advanced features.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does NeuronWriter cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">NeuronWriter starts at $23/month (Bronze, 25 analyses) and goes up to $97/month (Platinum, 100 analyses). Lifetime deals have previously been available through AppSumo. There's no free plan, but promotional trials are sometimes available through partner channels.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
