          <div class="faq-answer">Not really. NeuronWriter includes an AI writing assistant that can generate paragraphs and expand sections, but it doesn't produce complete, publish-ready articles. You still need a writer — human or AI — to do the heavy lifting. It's an optimization layer, not a content creation engine.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
