          <div class="faq-answer">NeuronWriter covers core NLP optimization for $23/month vs. Surfer's $119/month — that's the main argument for it. But Surfer has Google Docs integration, AI Visibility Tracking, better SERP data depth, and a more mature product. If budget is the constraint, NeuronWriter wins. If quality and workflow matter more, Surfer wins.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does NeuronWriter have a free trial?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">No permanent free plan. Limited free testing is available on the website. Full access requires a paid subscription. Promotional trials have appeared through partner channels and AppSumo deals.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does NeuronWriter handle local SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
